This is the script of  an online decision making task that has written with oTree software.
This file consists of 5 apps, one setting.py, and one query_join.py code. 
5 apps including: 1. consent 2. intro_hide_and_seek_2options (which is the main game) 3. introduction 4. question 5. wait 
the setting.py is for running the whole game, setting up the name of the game, room and other important parameters and its necessary for running the game. 
query_join.py is an example for getting query from Heroku server using python.
